note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Gryphon, Marie. \"The Affirmative Action Myth.\" Cato Institute, 2005. Retrieved December 05, 2016.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Gryphon, Marie. \"The Affirmative Action Myth.\" Cato Institute, 2005. Retrieved December 05, 2016.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-11\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Gryphon, Marie. \"The Affirmative Action Myth.\" Cato Institute, 2005. Retrieved December 05, 2016.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-12\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-12\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Sowell, Thomas. \"Affirmative Action around the World: An Empirical Study.\" New Haven: Yale University Press, 2004. p. 159. Retrieved December 05, 2016.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw2196\nCached time: 20180921034326\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: true\nCPU time usage: 0.104 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.138 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 363/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 11493/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 130/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 1/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 7067/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 0/400\nLua time usage: 0.046/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 2.48 MB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  119.377      1 -total\n 52.17%   62.284      1 Template:Reflist\n 41.88%   49.993      1 Template:Orphan\n 31.67%   37.804      3 Template:Cite_web\n 28.81%   34.397      1 Template:Ambox\n  4.82%    5.755      1 Template:Cite_book\n  1